Job Description
Must be fluent in English (writing & speaking). A proven track record of success in closing sales deals. Working knowledge of MS office, Outlook, Excel, Access and the Internet. Successful candidate must have a strong interest in technology, computers and IT products. Ability to effectively present information and respond to questions from clients and potential customers. Strong time management and organisational skills. Ability to multi-task in a fast paced environment. Working knowledge in the use of word processing, spreadsheet, Internet and e-mail
Job Specification
Maintain partners business and provide sales services including quote and pricing info. Company will provide a warm and hot target list, but some cold prospecting is required. Attend webinars and various other training to keep up to date with products and programs. Call clients and leads to introduce emerging technologies.
